text: Ceranemota is a genus of moths belonging to the subfamily Thyatirinae of the Drepanidae. ==Species== * Ceranemota improvisa Edwards, 1873 * Ceranemota fasciata Barnes & McDunnough, 1910 * Ceranemota crumbi Benjamin, 1938 * Ceranemota semifasciata Benjamin, 1938 * Ceranemota tearlei Edwards, 1888 * Ceranemota partida Clarke, 1938 * Ceranemota albertae Clarke, 1938 * Ceranemota amplifascia Clarke, 1938 ==References== Category:Thyatirinae Category:Drepanidae genera
title: Ceranemota
